## Overview

This document provides guidelines for using the rules framework with various AI coding assistants (Claude, GitHub Copilot, ChatGPT, Cursor, etc.) and IDEs (VS Code, Codium, Replit, etc.). These rules are designed to be IDE-agnostic and AI-tool agnostic.

## Automatic Rule Discovery

